 Ishizuka Kofun]][[Category:qq]] [[en:Makimuku Ishizuka Kofun]][[Category:11]][[Category:11]][[Category:11]][[Category:bump1-19]] [[Category:11]][[Category:refreshing categories imported on 2024-01-19]] [[Category:11]][[Category:bump 1-26]] [[Category:Fixed Kofun templates]]
