It is dated to around 180CE, with the nearby [[:en:Makimuku Katsuyama Kofun|Makimuku Katsuyama Kofun]] being dated to around [[200|200AD]].<ref>https://seaa-web.org/sites/default/files/publications/bseaa-1/BSEAA1-Rew-Styles.pdf</ref>
