ection]] of the deceased. Similar wooden and clay figures resembling roosters have been found in other early [[Kofun period]] tombs.<ref name="Ishino-1992a" /> Roosters are the [[Shinshi|animal messengers]] of [[Amaterasu]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=D |first=John |date=2011-07-28 |title=Power animals |url=https://www.greenshinto.com/2011/07/28/power-animals/ |access-date=2023-04-12 |website=Green Shinto |language=en-GB}}</ref>
